October 21, 2002

NOTE:
This profile requires the following key binds in Settings->Player Controls->Communication Controls:

G: Radio
H: Hand Signals
Y: Squad Radio
U: Shout
I: Whisper
L: Global

If you already have commands bound to those keys and don't want to change them, you will need to 
edit this file to make it work.  In the "<sequence keys" areas, replace the first letter with the
key you use for that comms command.  For example, if you use the P key for radio commands, replace:

     <sequence keys="g7" />

with:

     <sequence keys="p7" />

You'll also need to replace the G in the:

     <sequence keys="g``" delay="20" />

command with P (or whatever key you are using).

Feel free to edit this file and redistribute it, just please give credit where due.

Hooah!
-->

